### ========================================
### 学生管理接口测试 (StudentController)
### ========================================

### 1. 查询所有学生
GET http://localhost:8080/student/list/all

### 2. 根据学号查询学生
GET http://localhost:8080/student/info/20240001

### 3. 根据学号查询学生（不存在的学号）
GET http://localhost:8080/student/info/99999999

### 4. 根据班级查询学生
GET http://localhost:8080/student/list/byClass?className=软件1班

### 5. 分页查询学生
GET http://localhost:8080/student/list?page=1

### 6. 分页查询学生（指定班级）
GET http://localhost:8080/student/list?className=软件1班&page=1

### 7. 新增学生（POST请求）
POST http://localhost:8080/student/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "20240010",
  "name": "测试学生",
  "major": "软件工程",
  "className": "软件3班",
  "phone": "13800138010",
  "email": "test10@example.com"
}

### 8. 新增学生（学号重复，应该失败）
POST http://localhost:8080/student/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "20240001",
  "name": "重复学生",
  "major": "软件工程",
  "className": "软件1班",
  "phone": "13800138001",
  "email": "repeat@example.com"
}

### 9. 更新学生信息
PUT http://localhost:8080/student/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "20240010",
  "name": "修改后的名字",
  "major": "软件工程",
  "className": "软件3班",
  "phone": "13800138888",
  "email": "updated@example.com"
}

### 10. 删除学生
DELETE http://localhost:8080/student/delete/20240010


### ========================================
### 考勤管理接口测试 (AttendanceController)
### ========================================

### 11. 根据学生学号查询考勤记录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/student/20240001

### 12. 根据课程ID查询考勤记录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/course/1

### 13. 查询今日考勤记录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/date

### 14. 查询指定日期考勤记录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/date?date=2026-04-15

### 15. 查询学生某课程的所有考勤
GET http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/student/20240001/course/1

### 16. 统计某课程今日考勤人数
GET http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/count/course/1/date/2026-04-15

### 17. 统计学生迟到次数
GET http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/late/20240001/course/1

### 18. 签到（POST请求）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/checkin?studentId=20240001&courseId=1&status=正常

### 19. 签到（迟到）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/checkin?studentId=20240002&courseId=1&status=迟到

### 20. 签到（请假）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/checkin?studentId=20240003&courseId=1&status=请假

### 21. 添加考勤记录（完整信息）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "20240002",
  "studentName": "李四",
  "courseId": 1,
  "courseName": "数据结构",
  "attendanceDate": "2026-04-15",
  "status": "迟到",
  "checkInTime": "2026-04-15T09:15:00",
  "remark": "迟到15分钟"
}

### 22. 更新考勤记录
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "studentId": "20240001",
  "studentName": "张三",
  "courseId": 1,
  "courseName": "数据结构",
  "attendanceDate": "2026-04-15",
  "status": "请假",
  "remark": "病假"
}

### 23. 删除考勤记录
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/delete/1


### ========================================
### 用户管理接口测试 (UserController)
### ========================================

### 24. 查询所有教师
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/teachers

### 25. 查询所有用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/all

### 26. 根据ID查询用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/5

### 27. 根据用户名查询用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/username/testTeacher

### 28. 用户登录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/login?username=testTeacher&password=123456

### 29. 用户登录（密码错误）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/login?username=testTeacher&password=wrong

### 30. 注册新用户（POST）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newTeacher",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "teacher",
  "realName": "新老师",
  "teacherNo": "T2024008",
  "email": "new@test.com",
  "phone": "13900139008",
  "gender": "女",
  "department": "软件工程系"
}

### 31. 更新用户信息
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 5,
  "username": "testTeacher",
  "realName": "修改后的老师",
  "email": "updated@test.com",
  "phone": "13900139999",
  "gender": "女",
  "department": "计算机科学系",
  "status": 1
}

### 32. 删除用户
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/user/delete/5